name: I am a lemon
description: ‘I am a lemon’ shows the importance of affirmation words and how they are an important process of accepting yourself. By telling yourself: I am a lemon, you become your most free and pure self. ‘I am a lemon’ is the fourth nft in the second part of the lemon collection. The second part of the lemon collection tells the rest of the story in 6 illustrations. This part is about becoming and sharing the lemon. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
